Titolo: Ford Racing (video game)

Anno: 2000

Descrizione: Ford Racing is a racing video game published by Empire Interactive for Windows and the PlayStation video game console. The computer version was developed by Elite Systems and released on November 2, 2000, while the PlayStation version was developed by Toolbox Design and released on January 29, 2001.It was the first game in the Ford Racing video game series, and received mixed reviews. Ford Racing was released as a downloadable PS one Classic game on the PlayStation Store in May 2009, allowing it to be played on the PlayStation 3 and PlayStation Portable.